reviewText: Awesome! My husband and I completely enjoyed this great DVD! If you are a Duck fan, I think you will love it, and I think it would also be a great video to show to church groups, youth groups or to just share with friends or family. For the affordable price, it sure was worth every penny and more! Such a blessing to get to hear Phil share how he shares his faith in Christ! Love the Robertsons for that!!!
Shorter than I thought it would be.
Awesome Movie!! Uplifting, great for all ages, and also a great gift to give for spreading the Word of God!!!!
